{"tid":1993313,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"「只愛女友」TWICE搭肩也不心動","createTime":"2020-04-28T16:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T16:41:13.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1a19323f7ffe61d58591fb003e6d6bc7f99efe4","tid":1993313,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"韓10歲童星金康勳因韓劇《山茶花開時》受到廣大觀眾喜愛，知名典禮《MAMA》更邀請他擔任後台主持人，人氣不容小覷。小大人的他，曾公開有女友，但最近上節目坦言被甩，只因為回了對方「嗯嗯」2字，李尚敏就同情請喝汽水，笑翻所有人。 <br />\n<br />\n金康勳大方公開有女友，美貌神似Red Velvet的Irene，但他近期在節目《我家的熊孩子》跟李尚敏表示，因為很多誤會所以和女友分手2次，他解釋問了對方幾點睡，自己準備要睡的時候回了「嗯嗯」2字，然後就被甩了，李尚敏想安慰失戀的金康勳，掏錢請喝汽水，畫面十分搞笑。<br />\n<br />\n金康勳深受不少藝人喜愛，他去年12月擔任《MAMA》後台主持人，<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">TWICE見到他主動搭肩受訪，更詢問康勳是不是ONCE（TWICE粉絲名），他一秒否認</span></span></ins></strong>，但希望TWICE能喊一下朋友的名字，這樣朋友就會請他吃辣炒年糕，互動十分可愛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.nownews.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/1588081907-7aaf1a3ec47bf7343b9b5d904f03a8ba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nownews.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F1588081907-7aaf1a3ec47bf7343b9b5d904f03a8ba.png&h=c3443a20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金康勳（中）見到TWICE也不心動，坦承不是粉絲。（圖／M2 YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HB8igTyUZgQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHB8igTyUZgQ&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=c72252c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HB8igTyUZgQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VqkmicGPIbc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVqkmicGPIbc&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImPzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=41410b37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VqkmicGPIbc</a><br />\n<br />\n娜璉個柒婆想色誘！！<br />\n金康勳真男人！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7db04f29be9539bbf2a3dd407f9aace4bd24087b","tid":1993313,"uid":256952,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:25:06.000Z","msg":"樓主該該叫"},{"pid":"4c771bf856812e9e07ae1ff86a4c09aace01c4e3","tid":1993313,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:34:29.000Z","msg":"TWICE食榆檸檬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba81276e7e1b6ee0e8bd3e4ae20a5c94c5f77d2d","tid":1993313,"uid":138302,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:36:36.000Z","msg":"金康勳幾可愛"},{"pid":"10f58ecd6a3659e617379eaa60c1d8742842bff8","tid":1993313,"uid":60256,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"細路仔都唔like唱兒歌的Twice"},{"pid":"065e061934d955f3d17f7cc21d55d0bcf6e0846c","tid":1993313,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10f58ecd6a3659e617379eaa60c1d8742842bff8","tid":1993313,"uid":60256,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:37:12.000Z","msg":"細路仔都唔like唱兒歌的Twice"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:38:21.000Z","msg":"大人先中意聽兒歌"},{"pid":"22e1e7ee2809e030e1de19c8fdf673c7d55cec17","tid":1993313,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"佢好似係牙米"},{"pid":"54f848e4b56cb2266f0791ce1035295b3fdd313e","tid":1993313,"uid":137569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"大山婆對嘢真係好大"}]}